```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Dynamo Frontend] --> B[API Server]
    B --> C[Smart Router]
    C --> D[Disaggregated Workers]
    
    D --> E[vLLM Backend]
    D --> F[SGLang Backend]
    D --> G[TensorRT-LLM Backend]
    
    C --> H[KV Cache Manager]
    H --> I[Multi-tier Memory]
    
    J[Planner] --> K[Event Plane]
    K --> C
    
    L[NATS Server] --> K
    M[Etcd] --> J
```

### 

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class DistributedRuntime {
        +initialize()
        +register_component()
        +distribute_request()
    }
    
    class Frontend {
        +HTTP_Server
        +Router
        +Preprocessor
    }
    
    class Worker {
        +PrefillWorker
        +DecodeWorker
        +MultimodalWorker
    }
    
    class Router {
        +RoundRobin
        +Random
        +KV_Router
    }
    
    class KVCacheManager {
        +BlockManager
        +MemoryHierarchy
        +EventPublisher
    }
    
    DistributedRuntime --> Frontend
    DistributedRuntime --> Worker
    Frontend --> Router
    Router --> KVCacheManager
    Worker --> KVCacheManager
```

stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Initialization
    Initialization --> ModelLoading: Load Model
    ModelLoading --> Ready: Model Ready
    
    Ready --> RequestProcessing: New Request
    RequestProcessing --> KVCacheLookup: Check Cache
    KVCacheLookup --> CacheHit: Cache Found
    KVCacheLookup --> CacheMiss: Cache Miss
    
    CacheHit --> WorkerSelection: Select Worker
    CacheMiss --> PrefillWorker: Process Prefill
    PrefillWorker --> WorkerSelection: Prefill Complete
    
    WorkerSelection --> DecodeWorker: Select Decode
    DecodeWorker --> ResponseGeneration: Generate Response
    ResponseGeneration --> Ready: Response Sent
